{"word":"φοινίσσω","slug":"φοινίσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φοινίσσω</b></el> <el>(φοινίσσω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φοινός'><el>φοινός</el></a>\n<p/><i>to redden, make red</i>, Orac. <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be</i> or <i>become red</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}